task.summary: Contact form follows correct db structure and includes user name and trick name
Fixed issue with contact auth clashing with speed auth
Added incorrect level form and id getters and setters
Quickfix to include ids in all MainActivity submitted feedback
Added web app and contact icons to MainMenu
Replies can now be viewed from ContactActivity if the user is signed in
Expandable list group now includes desc and more padding
ContactActivity can now view all feedback and replies, and new replies can be made
Sign in from MainActivity dialog, and some minor fixes to ContactActivity
Automatically change name when signed in
Added ability to record and submit tricks directly to Firebase Storage
Choose video from gallery and in app size limit check
